6:
Tch! There's no end to these things!
Where do they keep coming from?!
9:
Indeed, the situation does not bode
well for us. We must find an opening
and break through somehow.
14:
Did someone call for a totally
kick-ass hero?!
20:
Here I go! Everything's locked and
loaded!
25:
Hahaha! Easy-peasy,
lemon-squeezy! You all right there?
28:
Thanks for the save! Your technique
was amazing!
32:
Heh-heh-heh. Dazzled? I don't
blame you! After all, you're looking
at Copperhead Kannon,
gun-meister extraordinaire!
37:
Forgive me, but I can't say I've heard
of you.
42:
Seriously?! That's weird. I've been
pretty active 'round these parts...
44:
Well, whatever! My reputation can
only grow from here! Soon everyone
and their grandmas will know my
name—
53:
Oh, sorry. That's just my stomach. All
my runnin' and gunnin's got me
starved!
58:
Really? Hmm, hang on. I think I've
got something in here...
62:
Do you like sandwiches? I know
they're not much in the way of
thanks, but—
72:
All right. Did everyone get one? Then
let's dig in!
77: Oh boy! Down the hatch you go!
89:
It was so good I couldn't help
myself! This is store-quality grub!
93:
Know what? You totally should open
a shop! I bet you could make a
fortune!
97:
I know this is weird comin' from us,
but you're awfully relaxed
considering what we went through
back there...
101:
You are an excellent markswoman,
however.
105:
I agree. It was especially impressive
considering your weapons were in
energy saver mode.
113:
From what I can see, your weapon
has the potential to deal greater
damage.
116: R-really? Hold on, let me give it a try...
121: Try the release here on the left.
128: Whoa! It's like a whole new gun!
130:
Ahaha... Come to think of it, I did
wonder if my shots weren't getting
weaker. I must've changed the
settings by accident.
135:
How do you not notice turning your
gun into a peashooter?!
143:
You're amazing, you know that? You
figured out what was broken at a
glance!
146:
Nothing was broken. The issue was
the settings.
151:
Awesome! That decides things!
Make room, 'cause you've got
yourself a new traveling companion!
153:
You saw what I can do, right? If you
need extra firepower, I'm your gal!
157:
I don't mind, but are you sure you
want to make a huge decision like
that on the spot?
161:
It's fiiine! The more the merrier and
all that, right?
163:
Sides, if my gun gets busted again,
I'll know who to ask! And this is so
much cooler than my old job.
166:
Not to mention the food you had
was delicious! I'll go anywhere if it's
for good grub!
172:
Geez, how do we keep collecting
these weirdos?
